### 2. `.gitignore`
This prevents "junk" files, temporary test files, and Python cache from being uploaded to your GitHub.

```text
# Python 
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
ENV/

# MRI Test Files
*.tmp
*.nii.gz
*.nii
*.dicom

# OS Specific
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# WSL/Configuration backups
.wslconfig.bak